{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"readonly","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackState","text":"MLNOfflinePackState","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@E@MLNOfflinePackState"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"state","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The state of an inactive or completed pack is computed lazily and is set to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackState\/MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" by default. To request the pack’s status, use"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-requestProgress"},{"type":"text","text":" method. To get notified when the state becomes known and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"when it changes, observe KVO change notifications on this pack’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"state"},{"type":"text","text":" key"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"path. Alternatively, you can add an observer for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"s about this pack that come from the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"default notification center."}]}]}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The pack’s current state."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/state"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/state"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"fragments":[{"text":"state","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"state"}],"role":"symbol","title":"state","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflinePack(py)state","symbolKind":"property","roleHeading":"Instance Property"},"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage":{"type":"topic","title":"MLNOfflineStorage","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"MLNOfflineStorage implements a singleton (shared object) that manages offline"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"packs and ambient caching. All of this class’s instance methods are asynchronous,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"reflecting the fact that offline resources are stored in a database. The shared"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object maintains a canonical collection of offline packs in its "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"packs"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflineStorage"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack/state":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/state","abstract":[{"text":"The pack’s current state.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"state"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/Ma